## Work Completed

### 1. Implemented Role-Based Administration

Created new administrative groups and users to simulate real organizational roles.

Administrative Accounts:

- labadmin
- helpdesk01 (Tier 1)
- helpdesk02 (Tier 2)

Administrative Group Model:

- GG_Aether_Helpdesk_T1
- GG_Aether_Helpdesk_T2

Organizational Design:

- Admin accounts remain in `OU=Admins`
- Managed users remain in delegated user containers

Key realization:

Delegation is applied to the OU containing managed objects—not the OU containing the administrators.

This clarified the separation between:

- administrative identities
- managed identities
- delegated resource boundaries

